            "description": "For my bachelor research project I performed experiments with a sloshing water tank at the Royal Netherlands Institute for Sea Research (NIOZ) under supervision of Leo Maas. I investigated how the frequency of the higher harmonics depend on water depth, length of the water tank and the driving frequency. I also performed some experiments with sloping walls in the water tank and placed some obstacles in the water tank. The experiments were filmed with a camera and the analysis of the filmed water levels were done in Matlab.\n\nGrade: 8.5",
